node.label: In (FireStatus RL #2)
node.description: The input signal to be processed.

object.script:
function onTick() rocketCounter = input.getNumber(1) cooldown = math.max(0, input.getNumber(2)-1)
FireAt1 = false FireAt2 = false FireAt3 = false
RLStatus1 = input.getBool(1) RLStatus2 = input.getBool(2) RLStatus3 = input.getBool(3) FIRE = input.getBool(4)
if FIRE==true and cooldown==0 then if RLStatus1 == true then FireAt1 = true cooldown = 5 rocketCounter = math.max(0, rocketCounter-1) elseif RLStatus2 == true then FireAt2 = true cooldown = 5 rocketCounter = math.max(0, rocketCounter-1) elseif RLStatus3 == true then FireAt3 = true cooldown = 5 rocketCounter = math.max(0, rocketCounter-1) end end
output.setBool(1, FireAt1) output.setBool(2, FireAt2) output.setBool(3, FireAt3)
output.setNumber(1, rocketCounter) output.setNumber(2, cooldown) end
